    "body": "Something we should document is how we handle requires/imports\r\n\r\nHow to choose from import/require:\r\n1. If the module loads fast: ESM import\r\n2. If not, import/require locally.\r\n2.1 Are we in a sync function: use node's `require`\r\n2.1 Are we in an async function: use `await import`\r\n3. If the import is only for side-effects: user node's `require`",
